casebody.data:
Pamela Jean BARBOUR, Employee
v.
Raj RATHORE d/b/a Luxury Inn, Employer, Non-Insured. No. 625P03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2004. Rajendra S. Rathore, Pro Se. Robert Lucas, for Pamela Jean Barbour.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 2nd day of December 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the Order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2004."
